earch,咁佢search 緊時佢就會有訊號發出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"咩係<span style=\"color: red;\">設備接收既訊號</span>"},{"pid":"b06169e4587e924b0ca53ddc3d9158c6f3129d44","tid":754630,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"search 緊時佢就會有訊號發出[/quote]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"22c65f6163236e573830385ef59bd78b195ea792","tid":754630,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3bd31882e82ad8223978e93d11d14d4712f09f3","tid":754630,"uid":50574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f6896f7cc69aa3f61e8730d2131baa1b115f9b9","tid":754630,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T21:32:10.000Z","msg":"唔係呀 ，我地平時見到Search到既係router發出既訊號.<br />\n我想要既係設備接收既訊號，即係你電話要搵wifi時佢會不停search,咁佢search 緊時佢就會有訊號發出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"咩係<span style=\"color: red;\">設備接收既訊號</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"樓上巴打講左，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e14dacf9f5a44cb5a1230b053566138ce50092","tid":754630,"uid":56895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"自己買個旅行 ap ，mod firmware 可能仲簡單"},{"pid":"25fbb52cfb1f22c02c147184c4482435b3809b29","tid":754630,"uid":148497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係呀 ，我地平時見到Search到既係router發出既訊號.<br />\n我想要既係設備接收既訊號，即係你電話要搵wifi時佢會不停search,咁<span style=\"color: red;\">佢search 緊時佢就會有訊號發出</span></blockquote><br />\n睇黎。。。你好似唔係好知道wifi發射同接收嘅原理，<br />\nwifi發射器（例如router）發出嘅wifi信號，其實係電磁波一種，<br />\n而接收器（例如電話）都係會發出電磁波，<br />\n係我地周圍好多物品都會發出電磁波。<br />\n電磁波透過大氣傳送，會根據周圍環境改變傳送強弱。<br />\n<br />\n因為大氣中有好多唔同嘅電磁波，所以有好多唔同嘅識別碼，<br />\n至於接收一方點解收到wifi信號，<br />\n因為發射一方發出ESSID信號供接收一方檢測可用網路。<br />\n<br />\nwifi信號強弱睇發射器（例如router）而定，<br />\n發射電磁波愈強，wifi信號愈強。<br />\n而接收器（例如電話）接收信號強弱同樣道理。<br />\nwifi距離基本就係100米左右，無阻礙情況下，愈近愈強，<br />\n因此你身邊如果有wifi發射器（例如router ABC），<br />\n搜尋wifi信號時router ABC都會係第1個，因為wifi信號最強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">你紅字嗰段</span>，係唔係想講電磁波？<br />\n至於探測電磁波嘅APPS如下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?ei=uq9YW-GzI8Gj-QaHtbKYBg&amp;q=%E6%8E%A2%E6%B8%AC%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2+APPS&amp;oq=%E6%8E%A2%E6%B8%AC%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2+APPS&amp;gs_l=psy-ab.3...1529.2675.0.3249.5.5.0.0.0.0.70.235.5.5.0....0...1c.1.64.psy-ab..0.0.0....0.q_laT27nYlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fei%3Duq9YW-GzI8Gj-QaHtbKYBg%26q%3D%25E6%258E%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25A3%2581%25E6%25B3%25A2%2BAPPS%26oq%3D%25E6%258E%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25A3%2581%25E6%25B3%25A2%2BAPPS%26gs_l%3Dpsy-ab.3...1529.2675.0.3249.5.5.0.0.0.0.70.235.5.5.0....0...1c.1.64.psy-ab..0.0.0....0.q_laT27nYlc&d=6AKR81sUGUeq1ap08EE1ctU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c609fc6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?ei=uq9YW-GzI8Gj-QaHtbKYBg&amp;q=%E6%8E%A2%E6%B8%AC%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2+APPS&amp;oq=%E6%8E%A2%E6%B8%AC%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2+APPS&amp;gs_l=psy-ab.3...1529.2675.0.3249.5.5.0.0.0.0.70.235.5.5.0....0...1c.1.64.psy-ab..0.0.0....0.q_laT27nYlc</a>"},{"pid":"ffe9b074d88c5a1e3fbbdff989ced3b494036643","tid":754630,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e14dacf9f5a44cb5a1230b053566138ce50092","tid":754630,"uid":56895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"自己買個旅行 ap ，mod firmware 可能仲簡單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:01:34.000Z","msg":"巴打 你好似明明地 可唔可以教我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1e7de94c6011d362fdc0877b342ca41c901a73","tid":754630,"uid":56895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffe9b074d88c5a1e3fbbdff989ced3b494036643","tid":754630,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"